{{col-2-of-2}}
===1910s=== * D.W. Griffith's ''[[Intolerance (film)|Intolerance]]''<ref>Boston Globe, Feb. 2, 1918</ref>
===1920s=== * [[Monroe Salisbury]] and [[Shirley Mason (actress)|Shirley Mason]] in "new photoplays"<ref>Boston Globe, Feb. 10, 1920</ref> * ''[[Smilin' Through (1922 film)]]''<ref>Boston Globe, Dec. 12, 1922</ref> {{col-end}}
